.env
node_modules/
# Google credentials — SECRET, never commit
google-sa.json
*.sa.json
*-service-account*.json
google-oauth-client.json
google-oauth-token.json
# Keep example.com.json as a template; ignore your real site configs if they contain anything sensitive.
# (IDs aren't secret, so by default real configs ARE committed. Uncomment to ignore them:)
# sites/*.json
# !sites/example.com.json
